           class="rb allrecipes" >
        </form>
      </div>
      <div id="recipeTopSection">
        <h2> Healthy Starts With Food! </h2>
        <h3>
         Healthy eating is the foundation for a vibrant life. By choosing nutritious and balanced meals, we nourish our bodies and enhance overall well-being. Incorporating fresh fruits, vegetables, whole grains, lean proteins, and healthy fats into our diet promotes optimal health. It's essential to prioritize portion control and avoid processed foods, excessive sugar, and unhealthy fats. Embracing healthy eating habits can boost energy levels, support weight management, strengthen the immune system, and reduce the risk of chronic diseases.
        </h3>
      </div>
      <!-- FOOD WHEEL SIDE IMAGE -->
      <div id="recipeMidSection">
        <img
          src="/images/foodGroups.png"
          class="foodWheel"
          alt="Food Wheel Image"
        />

        <div id="recipeCatalog">
     

          <h1>Search For A Recipe!</h1>

          <img src="/images/recipeMainImage.jpeg" class="recipeMainImage" />

          <form action="/recipeItems" method="post">
            <input
              type="text"
              name="query"
              id="recipeSearch"
              placeholder="Find A Recipe"
            />
            <button type="submit" class=" rb button2">Search</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="recipeTopSection">
        <!-- <h2>Nutrition is a Key Component for Your Health</h2> -->
        <h3>
          Proper nutrition involves consuming a variety of fruits, vegetables, whole grains, lean proteins, and healthy fats. These foods provide essential nutrients like vitamins, minerals, and antioxidants, supporting optimal health and reducing the risk of diseases like heart disease and cancer.
        </h3>
      </div>

      <div class="favRecipesCardsContainer">
        <div class="favRecipesCards">
          <div class="desc calories">
          
          </div>
          
          <img
            src="/images/healthyFood.png"
            alt="An Image of Food"
            class="favImage"
          />
          <div class="favRecipeHolder">
            <h5 id="favRecipeText">What You Put In Your Body</h5>
            <p class="recipeText">
              Everything you eat and drink affects you in different ways. It can
              nourish and support your body and brain or it can be a toxin. By
              learning how different foods, beverages, and individual nutrients
              affect you, you can create a diet that supports your specific
              health goals.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="favRecipesCards">
          
          <img
            src="/images/selfcarerecipes.jpg"
            alt="An Image of Food"
            class="favImage"
          />
          <div class="favRecipeHolder">
            <h5 id="favRecipeText">What You Put On Your Body</h5>
            <p class="recipeText">
              What’s in the lotions, hair products, and makeup you put on your
              body? Or the air fresheners and cleaning products you breathe in
              every day? Many of these have ingredients that affect your
              hormones and damage your DNA. Replacing these everyday items with
              safer ones removes harmful toxins from your body.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="favRecipesCards">
          
          <img
            src="/images/restrecipe.jpeg"
            alt="An Image of Food"
            class="favImage"
          />
          <div class="favRecipeHolder">
            <h5 id="favRecipeText">How You Rest Your Body</h5>
            <p class="recipeText">
              Your body has to rest and recharge every day. Poor quality sleep
              and too much stress not only wear you down, but also affect
              everything from your hormonal balance to how your mind works.
              Improving your sleep and reducing stress has major trickle-down
              effects for your health.</p>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div> 
        <div class="favRecipesCards">
         
          <img
            src="/images/carerecipe.jpeg"
            alt="An Image of Food"
            class="favImage"
          />
          <div class="favRecipeHolder">
             <h5 id="favRecipeText">How You Care For Your Body</h5>
            <p class="recipeText">Healing is an ongoing, holistic process. That means to feel better, live better, and achieve better health, all of your parts — body, mind, and spirit — have to be in balance. You’ll learn how to identify the root problems that are causing your symptoms and implement ways to change them.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
     
